properties.fixme: This entrance happens into where the building is marked. The roof on the two parallel ways going into the building is open, but the way that connects the two is closed so it's marked as tunnel.

properties.note: This doorless entrance has a bollard; unclear how a mapper would map the entrance and bollard separately.
